  "body": "https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/19a65903062293a3ed67ff10fd80572b798caf93/contracts/token/ERC777/ERC777.sol#L373-L380\r\n\r\nSimilar to `_mint`, the `_burn` method may need to be called by a particular token's implementation when various events occur.  One _could_ work around this by making the token be its own operator, but that just seems silly and is a waste of gas.\r\n",
